title: 301 - Gassed Up
description:
I CAN. I WILL. I MUST. BE DEMANDING!
Do you really know what it means to be demanding? Have you earned the right to demanding in your home, work, school, or community? In this episode, through personal stories and anecdotes, the guys discuss and share what it truly means to be demanding. 
Listener Perks 


ORGANIFI  is giving our listeners up to 20% off of their order! Just go to www.organifi.com/success. Their superfood green juice powder allows you to get your greens anytime, anywhere while on the go.
